snippet.title: City Bus Manager | Official Release Date Teaser
snippet.description:
COMING SOON |  Steam: https://bit.ly/3STw8o9

Create your personal bus routes and build your own bus depot from scratch in City Bus Manager. Play your own home town or any famous city in the world with real map data. Buy buses, maintain them, take care of your staff and lead your bus company to become the #1 in town! 

For more news and information follow us: 
Discord: https://discord.gg/mUrB3gVC2T
Facebook: https://de-de.facebook.com/PeDePe.GbR
Twitter: https://twitter.com/aerosoftgmbh
